statements: SELECT * FROM user_interactions;
SELECT interaction_id, user_id, interaction_time FROM user_interactions ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type, platform_used FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'click';
SELECT user_id, action_taken FROM user_interactions WHERE platform_used = 'desktop';
SELECT user_id, interaction_details->'product_name' AS product_name FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_details->>'purchase_amount' > '50.00';
SELECT * FROM user_interactions WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001';

SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM user_interactions WHERE action_taken = 'like' AND interaction_type = 'post' AND platform_used = 'Android';
SELECT COUNT(interaction_id) AS total_interactions, platform_used FROM user_interactions GROUP BY platform_used HAVING COUNT(interaction_id) > 100;
SELECT interaction_time, interaction_details->>'location' AS location FROM user_interactions WHERE interaction_details->>'device_type' = 'mobile' ORDER BY interaction_time ASC LIMIT 5;
